original_title: The Goo Goo Dolls: Live in Alaska: Music in High Places
overview: Talk about unique adventure series -- this one takes top recording artists to the four corners of the globe and features exciting acoustic performances set against the backdrop of some of the most intriguing natural locations on Earth. Follow the Goo Goo Dolls as they discover the culture, history and spirituality of Alaska. Songs include: "Black Balloon," "Acoustic #3" and "Broadway."
title: The Goo Goo Dolls: Live in Alaska: Music in High Places
